From: Eric Yang <Eric.Yang2@amd.com>
Date: Wed, 28 Feb 2018 14:45:36 -0500
Subject: drm/amd/display: early return if not in vga mode in disable_vga
Git-commit: abca24007e0838ee8bfff37a188bf8df00703c52
Patch-mainline: v4.16-rc5
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166
No-fix: e18d3086733bd150f87594a754ae983329fb0ba1

The work around for hw bug causes S3 resume failure. Don't execute
disable vga logic if not in vga mode.

